ts-is-no-more&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199965/the-netflix-app-for-quest-headsets-is-no-more" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199965/the-netflix-app-for-quest-headsets-is-no-more</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-16T17:17:25-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-16T17:17:25-04:00</updated><title> Ozy Media 创始人卡洛斯·沃森犯有欺诈罪</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;2017 年活动期间，戴着墨镜的凯蒂·库里克 (Katie Couric) 站在卡洛斯·沃森 (Carlos Watson) 旁边，站在写着“Ozy Fest”的标牌前。” src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hOBSFbkgjljFSot0arxE4s4gRDI=/804x0:4550x2497/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73464656/820900644.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption >;Katie Couric（左）和 Ozy 首席执行官兼联合创始人 Carlos Watson 在 2017 年 Ozy Fest 期间登台演讲 |摄影：Bryan Bedder/Getty Images for Ozy Fusion Fest 2017&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;O4p5Vx&quot;>;Carlos Watson 和他共同创立的现已关闭的 Ozy Media 初创公司&lt;a href=&quot;https://www .justice.gov/usao-edny/pr/carlos-watson-Founder-and-former-ceo-ozy-media-inc-convicted-multi-million-dollar&quot;>;被联邦法院判定犯有欺诈罪&lt;/a>;周二陪审团，如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.nytimes.com/2024/07/16/business/media/carlos-watson-ozy-media-guilty.html?smid=nytcore-ios-share&amp;amp; referingSource=articleShare&amp;amp;sgrp=c-cb&quot;>;《纽约时报》早些时候报道过&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。在长达数周的审判过程中，陪审团听取了政府的指控，即 Ozy Media 通过伪造财务记录、夸大观众人数，甚至捏造商业交易来误导投资者。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;3jGyq6&quot; >;Ozy Media 前首席执行官沃森 (Watson) 于 2013 年与萨米尔·拉奥 (Samir Rao) 共同创立了该公司。该公司推出了在线杂志、时事通讯，并在纽约市举办了年度会议，同时达成了高调的合作伙伴关系和 &lt;a href=&quot; https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fmoney%2Fbusiness%2F2014%2F10%2F06%2Faxel-springer-investment- in-ozy%2F16764657%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F7%2F16%2F24199947%2Fozy-media-carlos-watson-found-guilty-fraud&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;获得数百万&lt;/a>;投资。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;1yJofV&quot;>;但是当 2021 年 &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.nytimes.com/2021/09/26/business/media/ozy-media-goldman-sachs.html&quot;>;来自《纽约时报》的文章&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;&lt;em>; &lt;/ em>;媒体专栏作家本·史密斯...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199947/ozy-media-carlos-watson-found-guilty -fraud&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199947/ozy-media-carlos-watson-found-guilty-fraud" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/16/24199947/ozy-media-carlos-watson-found-guilty-fraud</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry></feed>